            <thetext>Can a line be inserted in the logs whenever a mailbox is renamed/moved or deleted (which, using delayed delete, is effectively a rename anyway).

It&apos;s all too easy with a point-and-click client for a user to accidentally move a mailbox and not even realise for sometimes days afterwards. This has to be the biggest support request we get and the most difficult to track down because often the user doesn&apos;t know what the mailbox is called and invariably the mailbox has been moved between shared mailboxes and/or their inbox.</thetext>
